      <title>Singapore haze map for 24 June 2013</title>
      <link>http://vielmetti.github.io/post/2013/2013-06-24-singapore-haze-map-for-24-june-2013/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2013 23:36:37 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://vielmetti.github.io/post/2013/2013-06-24-singapore-haze-map-for-24-june-2013/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-23037409&#34; target=&#34;_self&#34;&gt;BBC World Service has reporting on the dense haze&lt;/a&gt; that&amp;rsquo;s covering Singapore and parts of Malaysia as a result of land-clearing fires in Indonesia. The &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.weather.gov.sg/wip/c/portal/layout?p_l_id=PUB.1003.538&#34; target=&#34;_self&#34;&gt;map below&lt;/a&gt; is from the Meteorological Service Singapore. The Indonesian president has &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.straitstimes.com/the-big-story/the-haze-singapore/story/haze-update-indonesias-yudhoyono-apologises-haze-20130624&#34; target=&#34;_self&#34;&gt;apologized&lt;/a&gt; for the haze, notes the Straits Times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;asset-img-link&#34; href=&#34;http://vielmetti.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4f1a53ef0192ab931d8f970d-pi&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8341c4f1a53ef0192ab931d8f970d&#34; style=&#34;width: 600px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;&#34; title=&#34;Singapore-haze-map-24-June-2013&#34; src=&#34;http://vielmetti.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4f1a53ef0192ab931d8f970d-600wi&#34; alt=&#34;Singapore-haze-map-24-June-2013&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Singaporeans are advised to wear masks when going outdoors, and to stay indoors if at all possible. SingPost has &lt;a href=&#34;http://postandparcel.info/56481/news/human-resources/singpost-hands-out-face-masks-as-air-pollution-reaches-hazardous-levels/&#34; target=&#34;_self&#34;&gt;issued masks&lt;/a&gt; for postal workers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
